<div class="row">
	<div class="span6 offset3">
		<h1>1 Year Chart Review</h1>
		<h2>Subject ID: <%= @followup1year.subject_id %></h2>
		<!-- http://railscasts.com/episodes/217-multistep-forms -->
		<%= form_for @followup1year, html: {"data-parsley-validate" => ''} do |f| %>
		<div id="crf_status">
			<p><i><strong>Please mark participant status</strong>. Please mark appropriately (for example, don't mark "Participant completed assessment" until you have finished the assessment).</i></p>
			<%= select(:followup1year, :fu1year_crf_status,
				[["",nil],
				["Participant completed assessment", 1],
				["Participant missed assessment but still enrolled", 2],
				["Participant formally withdrew", 3],
				["Participant lost to follow-up (unknown reason)", 4],
				["Participant did not begin intervention after randomization", 5],
				["Participant died", 6]], {}, :style => "width:auto") %>
		</div>
			<ol>
				<li>Study Assessment (time since Baseline): 12 Months</li>
				<strong>Since the last chart review...</strong>
				<li>Has there been a revision at the same level (e.g. TT to higher TT)?
					<%= select(:followup1year, :fu1year_fuq_2, [["",nil],["1 - Yes",1],["0 - No",0],["Refused", 1000]],{}, :style => "width:auto", :data => {:"parsley-trigger" => 'change'}, :required => '') %>
					<div id="followup1year_revision">
						<ol type="a">
							<li>If YES, mark time since original amputation surgery: <%= number_field(:followup1year, :fu1year_fuq_2a, :style => "width:auto") %> <i>(days)</i></li>
						</ol>
					</div>
				</li>
				<li>Has there been a revision to a higher level (e.g. TM to TT or TT to TF)?
					<%= select(:followup1year, :fu1year_fuq_3, [["",nil],["1 - Yes",1],["0 - No",0],["Refused", 1000]],{}, :style => "width:auto", :data => {:"parsley-trigger" => 'change'}, :required => '') %>
					<div id="followup1year_revision_higher">
						<ol type="a">
							<li>If YES, mark time since original amputation surgery: <%= number_field(:followup1year, :fu1year_fuq_3a, :style => "width:auto") %> <i>(days)</i></li>
						</ol>
					</div>
				</li>
				<li>Has there been a contralateral limb amputation? <%= select(:followup1year, :fu1year_fuq_4, [["",nil],["1 - Yes",1],["0 - No",0],["Refused", 1000]],{}, :style => "width:auto", :data => {:"parsley-trigger" => 'change'}, :required => '') %>
					<div id="followup1year_contra">
						<p><i>If YES, mark contralateral level and type</i></p>
						<ol type="a">
							<li>Level: <%= select(:followup1year, :fu1year_fuq_4a_level, [["",nil],["1 - TM",1],["2 - Midfoot",2],["3 - Symes",3],["4 - TT",4],["5 - Knee",5],["6 - TF",6],["Refused", 1000]],{}, :style => "width:auto")%></li>
							<li>Type: <%= select(:followup1year, :fu1year_fuq_4a_type,[["",nil],["Initial",1],["Revision",2],["Refused", 1000]],{}, :style => "width:auto")%></li>
							<li>Mark time since original amputation surgery <%= number_field(:followup1year, :fu1year_fuq_4b, :style => "width:auto") %> <i>(days)</i> </li>
						</ol>
					</div>
				</li>
				<li>Was the patient admitted to the hospital? <%= select(:followup1year, :fu1year_fuq_5,[["",nil],["1 - Yes",1],["0 - No",0],["Refused", 1000]],{}, :style => "width:auto", :data => {:"parsley-trigger" => 'change'}, :required => '') %>
					<div id="followup1year_hospital">
						<ol type="a">
							<li>If yes, reason for admission: <%= text_field(:followup1year, :fu1year_fuq_5a, :style => "width:auto") %></li>
						</ol>
					</div>
				</li>
				<li>Has the patient passed away? <%= select(:followup1year, :fu1year_fuq_6,[["",nil],["1 - Yes",1],["0 - No",0],["Refused", 1000]],{}, :style => "width:auto", :data => {:"parsley-trigger" => 'change'}, :required => '') %>
					<div id="followup1year_passed">
						<ol type="a">
							<li>If YES, mark time since original amputation surgery: <%= number_field(:followup1year, :fu1year_fuq_6a, :style => "width:auto") %></li>
						</ol>
					</div>
				</li>
				<li>Notes: <%= text_field(:followup1year, :fu1year_fuq_7, :style => "width:auto") %></li>
			</ol>
			<div style="width:200px; margin:auto;">
				<%= f.submit "Submit", class: "btn btn-large btn-primary" %>
			</div>
		<% end %>
	</div>
</div>
